Benghazi burner
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a thermette; a portable makeshift device for heating containers of water within an open-ended jacket fired usu. by petrol (HNZD).
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
